(9, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '<p>At the heart of all O&amp;M lies the equipment. Across the nation, this equipment varies greatly in age, size, type, model, fuel used, condition, etc. O&amp;M services mainly should address</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Present general equipment descriptions and operating principles and procedures, parameters for the major equipment types.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The key maintenance components of particular equipment.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Highlight important safety issues.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Cost and energy efficiency issues.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Highlights of water-related efficiency impacts and issues.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Recommended general O&amp;M activities in the form of checklists.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Analysis of case studies with issues and root cause analysis and remedial measures.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Trouble free operation with optimum output as expected by clients.</p><p>Above considerations are the main objectives of O&amp;M services, and with aiming at these objectives, our company takes up O&amp;M services and serve customers with expert man power network added with technical knowledge in the fields of Design, Commissioning, Operation, Maintenance and Overhauling of all the equipment.</p><p><b><u style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why SPEL for O &amp; M:</u></b><br></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SPEL offers a complete range of Operations &amp; Maintenance (O&amp;M) services to Industrial and Thermal power plants.&nbsp; SPEL having rich experi